name: Cookiee Kawaii
description: '''Vanice Brittany Palmer''' (born August 5, 1993), known professionally as '''Cookiee Kawaii''', is an American singer. She is best known for her song "Vibe (If I Back It Up)", which became popular on [[TikTok]] in 2020. After the song went viral, she signed to [[Empire Distribution|Empire]], and released her debut studio album, ''Vanice'', in 2021.
